Package: claymapR
Title: Mold clay maps of two or three dimensions to show polygon delineations
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Chris", "Madsen", "Paul", "Chris.Madsen@gov.bc.ca", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: This package wraps and combines {sf}, {terra}, {tidverse} and {rgl} functions that you can use to make two- or three-dimensional maps of polygon data.
License: `use_mit_license()`, `use_gpl3_license()` or friends to pick a
    license
